OL,3,CRough sleepers behind new film calling
OL,4,Cfor homelessness reform
OL,6,FThe world premiere of a film
OL,7,Fdocumenting homelessness in the UK is
OL,8,Fbeing held at Newcastle's Tyneside
OL,9,FCinema.
OL,11,FSomeone's Daughter, Someone's Son will
OL,12,Fbe shown on Thursday 8 February and
OL,13,Ffeatures former rough sleeper Earl
OL,14,FJohn Charlton from the North East.
OL,16,FThe documentary-style production calls
OL,17,Ffor reform in how homelessness and
OL,18,Frough sleeping is tackled.
