OL,3,CRough sleepers behind new film calling
OL,4,Cfor homelessness reform
OL,6,FMr Charlton continued: "I am the voice
OL,7,Ffor those who can't be here and I'm
OL,8,Falso the voice for those who aren't
OL,9,Fbeing heard. To many, I was invisible.
OL,11,F"People never heard my opinion or my
OL,12,Fvoice or cries for help when I needed
OL,13,Fsupport so I'm here for those who
OL,14,Faren't here any more and also those
OL,15,Fthat are here just to fight the
OL,16,Fstruggles.
OL,18,F"There are things we can do to stop
OL,19,Fpeople from being homeless."
