OL,3,CRough sleepers behind new film calling
OL,4,Cfor homelessness reform
OL,6,FThe new film is directed by Lorna
OL,7,FTucker, who became homeless herself
OL,8,Faged just 14. She spent two years on
OL,9,Fthe streets, sleeping under Waterloo
OL,10,FBridge in London, while spending time
OL,11,Fin and out of sheltered accommodation.
OL,13,FAcademy Award winner and national
OL,14,Ftreasure Colin Firth voices the
OL,15,Ffeature, which has received support
OL,16,Ffrom musicians Sam Fender and Bryan
OL,17,FAdams.
OL,19,FThe premiere follows a kickstarter
OL,20,Ffundraiser to launch the film, which
OL,21,Fraised #30,000.
