OL,3,CRough sleepers behind new film calling
OL,4,Cfor homelessness reform
OL,6,FDartmouth Films, which made the film,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've been touched by the
OL,8,Foutpouring of kindness and generosity
OL,9,Ffrom the public who've connected with
OL,10,FLorna and Earl's stories, and want to
OL,11,Factively make a difference to
OL,12,Fhomelessness by supporting our film.
OL,14,F"With the February release date now
OL,15,Fconfirmed, we have an even bigger
OL,16,Fplatform to raise awareness and talk
OL,17,Fabout solutions that get to the root
OL,18,Fof the systemic issues surrounding
OL,19,Fhomelessness.
