OL,6,F"We hope the film will be a valuable
OL,7,Ftool in the campaign to end
OL,8,Fhomelessness once and for all."
OL,10,FA government spokesperson for the
OL,11,FDepartment of Levelling Up, Housing
OL,12,Fand Communities said: "We are
OL,13,Fdetermined to end rough sleeping for
OL,14,Fgood and are working hand-in-hand with
OL,15,Fthe homelessness sector and other
OL,16,Fpartners to make sure people have a
OL,17,Froof over their head and the support
OL,18,Fto rebuild their lives.
